namedQuery insert --toClass ~.app.shared.location.State --queryName State.DefaultFinders --queryValue "select e from State e where e.systemInfo.activeStatus=1 and e.countryId LIKE :countryId and e.stateName LIKE :stateName and e.stateCode BETWEEN :minstateCode AND :maxstateCode and e.stateCodeChar2 LIKE :stateCodeChar2 and e.stateCodeChar3 LIKE :stateCodeChar3"
